answers.answer: There a couple of things - pregnancy, uti, diabetes, hormone imbalance. I'm sure your dr will sort it out. Have you done a test? I didn't get any symptoms til 8wks both pregnancies but every woman is different.
Probably pregnant. Do you want to be? :)
Yeah to  a point but it might also be a uti or blatter infection :/
